title: I lost my 10 year mystery gift
body: to day i login my account and i got 10 year mystery gift. But i don't have skin or icon . Pls check

replies.body: We're not done sending out gifts just yet.  The gifts are being sent individually per our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-).  There are a lot of accounts, so hang tight until this is all wrapped up!

If you got the mystery gift then it's in your inventory somewhere (maybe you forgot which skin you got?).
The Icon might not be there yet, I didn't get my Icon the same day I got the Kayle skin.
